# =============================================================================
# SUPABASE TYPE REGENERATION CONFIGURATION
# =============================================================================
# 
# To regenerate Supabase types, you need ONE of the following:
#
# Option 1 (Recommended): Set your Supabase URL
# The script will extract the project ID automatically
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://yourproject.supabase.co
#
# Option 2: Set the project ID directly
# Find this in your Supabase Dashboard under Project Settings
# SUPABASE_PROJECT_ID=your-project-id-here
#
# Option 3: Use a direct database connection string
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:password@db.yourproject.supabase.co:5432/postgres
#
# Then run:
#   npm run types:generate
#
# =============================================================================

# Example (uncomment and replace with your values):
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://mthwfldcjvpxjtmrqkqm.supabase.co
# SUPABASE_PROJECT_ID=mthwfldcjvpxjtmrqkqm
